---
title: Indian Coconut, Lentil & Roast Cauliflower Bowl with Toasted Almonds & Pickled Onion
description: Enjoy an exciting meatless Monday by whipping up this wholesome bowl of lentils. Along with gently spiced cauliflower and a touch of zing thanks to the pickled onion, this is a veggie delight sent from the heavens.
